{
  "texts": [
    "• We discuss and compare the most popular deep learning-based image and video watermarking techniques to give researchers a clear understanding of the practical challenges of deep learning-based watermarking.",
    "• We also present some future directions for deep learning-based video watermarking.The rest of the paper is organized as follows.",
    "In Sect. 2, we introduce a review of the traditional image and video watermarking techniques by classifying them based on the embedding target and the used domain.",
    "Section 3 presents a comparison of image watermarking techniques utilizing deep learning methods, focusing on their network architecture.",
    "The next section details the small number of existing deep learningbased video watermarking techniques and shows their advantages."
  ]
}